00:00:28.840 --> 00:00:30.310
in significant ways and many dying

00:00:30.310 --> 00:00:32.210
as a result of the coronavirus pandemic.

00:00:32.210 --> 00:00:34.010
And that leaves many wondering

00:00:34.010 --> 00:00:36.150
