00:10:53.180 --> 00:10:54.300
Well, maybe.

00:10:54.300 --> 00:10:56.290
Some have argued that Fox News

00:10:56.290 --> 00:10:58.440
as well as other cable news channels

00:10:58.440 --> 00:11:01.420
have promoted incorrect
information, misleading comments,

00:11:01.420 --> 00:11:04.420
and other conspiracy theories
that have been detrimental

00:11:04.420 --> 00:11:07.120
to actually fighting the
